    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0825c06"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>武陵開元寺<persName key="A012161">慧昭</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0825c07"/><persName key="A012161">釋慧昭</persName>，未詳何許人。其為僧也，性僻而高，<lb
ed="T" n="0825c08"/>恒修禪定，貌頗衰羸，好言人之休戚，而皆<lb
ed="T" n="0825c09"/>必中。與人交言，且不馴狎。閉關自處，左右<lb
ed="T" n="0825c10"/>無侍童。每日乞食，里人有八十餘者云：「<persName key="A012161"><persName key="A012161">昭</persName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0825c11"/>居此六十餘年，其容貌無異於少時昔日<lb
ed="T" n="0825c12"/>也。」但不知其甲子。<date notBefore-iso="+0806-01-29" key="j20154742020606" notAfter-iso="+0820-02-17"><name>元和</name>中</date>有<persName key="A012163">陳廣</persName>者，由孝<lb
ed="T" n="0825c13"/>廉調為<placeName key="PL000000029412">武陵</placeName>官，而酷好浮圖氏。一日因詣<lb
ed="T" n="0825c14"/><placeName key="PL000000029396">寺</placeName>，盡訪諸僧，<persName key="A012161">昭</persName>見<persName key="A012163">廣</persName>，且悲且喜曰：「<persName key="A012163">陳君</persName>何<lb
ed="T" n="0825c15"/>來之晚乎？」<persName key="A012163">廣</persName>愕然，自揣平生不識此<persName key="A012161">僧</persName>，何<lb
ed="T" n="0825c16"/>言來晚？乃曰：「未甞與<persName key="A012161">師</persName>遊，何責遲暮？」<persName key="A012161">昭</persName>曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0825c17"/>「此非倉卒可言，當為子一夕靜話，方盡此<lb
ed="T" n="0825c18"/>意。」<persName key="A012163">廣</persName>甚驚異，後時詣<persName key="A012161">昭</persName>宿，因請其事。<persName key="A012161">昭</persName>曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0825c19"/>「我劉氏子，宋孝<persName key="A002604">文帝</persName>之玄孫也。曾祖<placeName key="PL000000020179">鄱陽</placeName>王<lb
ed="T" n="0825c20"/><persName key="A012164">休業</persName>、祖<persName key="A012165">士弘</persName>，並詳於史氏。先人文學自負，<lb
ed="T" n="0825c21"/>為<persName key="A002655">齊竟陵王子良</persName>所知。<persName key="A002655">子良</persName>招集賢俊文學<lb
ed="T" n="0825c22"/>之士，而先人預焉。後仕齊梁之間，為<placeName key="PL000000013242">會稽</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0825c23"/>令。<persName key="A012161">吾</persName>生於<date from-iso="+0526-05-29" key="j19133261913354" to-iso="+0526-06-26">梁普通七年夏五月</date>，<date key="j19237701924134" from-iso="+0555-01-01" to-iso="+0555-12-31">年三十</date>方仕<lb
ed="T" n="0825c24"/>於陳，至<persName key="A004306">宣帝</persName>時為卑官，不為人知，徒與<lb
ed="T" n="0825c25"/><persName key="A012166">沈彥文</persName>為詩酒之交。後<placeName key="PL000000028643">長沙</placeName>王<persName key="A012167">叔堅</persName>與<persName key="A012168">始興<lb
ed="T" n="0825c26"/>王叔陵</persName>皆多聚賓客，大為聲勢，各恃權寵，<lb
ed="T" n="0825c27"/>有不平心。<persName key="A012161">吾</persName>與<persName key="A012166">彥文</persName>俱在<persName key="A012167">長沙</persName>之門下。及<lb
ed="T" n="0825c28"/><persName key="A012168">叔陵</persName>被誅，<persName key="A012161">吾</persName>懼不免，因皆銷聲匿跡<anchor xml:id="beg0825005"/>於<anchor xml:id="end0825005"/><lb
ed="T" n="0825c29"/>林谷，拾橡栗而食，掬溪㵎而飲，衣一短<pb ed="T" n="0826a" xml:id="T50.2061.0826a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0826a01"/>褐，雖寒暑不易，以待所憂之所定。無何<ptr type="glossary" target="#g493"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0826a02"/>有一老沙門至<persName key="A012161">吾</persName>所居曰：『<persName key="A012161">子</persName>骨法甚奇，當<lb
ed="T" n="0826a03"/>無疾耳。』<persName key="A012166">彥文</persName>再拜請其藥，曰：『<persName key="A012166">子</persName>無<persName key="A012161">劉君</persName>之<lb
ed="T" n="0826a04"/>壽，奈何？雖服<persName key="A012161">吾</persName>藥，亦無所補。』遂告別，將<lb
ed="T" n="0826a05"/>去，復謂<persName key="A012161">我</persName>曰：『塵俗以名利相勝，竟何有<lb
ed="T" n="0826a06"/>哉？唯釋氏可以捨此矣。』恭納其言，自是不<lb
ed="T" n="0826a07"/>知人事，凡十五年。又與<persName key="A012166">彥文</persName>俱至<placeName key="PL000000008975">建業</placeName>，時<lb
ed="T" n="0826a08"/>陳氏已亡，宮闕盡毀。<placeName key="PL000000008617">臺城</placeName>牢落，荊榛蔽路，<placeName key="PL000000009119">景<lb
ed="T" n="0826a09"/>陽<anchor xml:id="beg0826001"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>并</sic><corr>井</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0826001"/></placeName>塞，結綺基頹，文物衣冠，蕩然而盡。故老<lb
ed="T" n="0826a10"/>相遇，相携而泣，且曰：『一人無良，已至於是，<lb
ed="T" n="0826a11"/>隋氏所滅，良可悲乎！』又聞<persName key="A004597">後主</persName>及諸王皆入<lb
ed="T" n="0826a12"/><placeName key="PL000000042389">長安</placeName>，乃率<persName key="A012166">沈</persName>挈一囊乞食於路，以至<placeName key="PL000000042002">關中</placeName>。<lb
ed="T" n="0826a13"/><persName key="A012161">吾</persName><persName key="A012167">長沙王</persName>之故客也，恩遇甚厚，聞其遷往<placeName key="PL000000045676">瓜<lb
ed="T" n="0826a14"/>州</placeName>，則徑往就謁。<persName key="A012167">長沙王</persName>長於綺紈而早貴盛，<lb
ed="T" n="0826a15"/>雖流放之際，尚不事生業。時方與<persName key="A012171">沈妃</persName>酣<lb
ed="T" n="0826a16"/>飲。<persName key="A012161">吾</persName>與<persName key="A012166">沈</persName>再拜於前，<persName key="A012167">長沙</persName>悲慟，久之瀝泣<lb
ed="T" n="0826a17"/>而起，乃謂<persName key="A012161">吾</persName>曰：『一日家國淪亡，骨肉播遷，豈<lb
ed="T" n="0826a18"/>非天乎？』<persName key="A012161">吾</persName>自此且留<placeName key="PL000000045675">晉昌</placeName>，氐羌之塞。數年<lb
ed="T" n="0826a19"/>而<persName key="A012167">長沙</persName>殂，又數年<persName key="A012166">彥文</persName>亡，<persName key="A012161">吾</persName>因剔䰂為僧，<lb
ed="T" n="0826a20"/>遁跡<placeName key="PL000000013158">會稽山</placeName>佛寺，凡二十年，時已<date key="j19493371949701" from-iso="+0625-01-01" to-iso="+0625-12-31">百歲</date>矣。<lb
ed="T" n="0826a21"/>雖容體枯瘠，而筋力不衰。尚日行百里。因<lb
ed="T" n="0826a22"/>與一僧同至<placeName key="PL000000042189">長安</placeName>，時<persName key="A004630">唐高祖</persName>已有天下，建<lb
ed="T" n="0826a23"/>號武德。<date from-iso="+0623-02-08" key="j19486441948998" to-iso="+0624-01-28">至六年</date>，<persName key="A012161">吾</persName>自此或居<placeName key="PL000000042189">京</placeName><placeName key="PL000000023581">洛</placeName>，或遊<placeName key="PL000000000197">江<lb
ed="T" n="0826a24"/>左</placeName>，至於<placeName key="PL000000034650">三蜀</placeName><placeName key="PL000000000191">五嶺</placeName>，無不住焉，殆今<date key="j20187332019097" from-iso="+0815-01-01" to-iso="+0815-12-31">二百九<lb
ed="T" n="0826a25"/>十年</date>矣。雖烈寒酷熱，未甞有微恙。<date notBefore-iso="+0800-02-27" key="j20133112015139" notAfter-iso="+0805-02-28"><name>貞元</name>末</date>，<lb
ed="T" n="0826a26"/>於此<placeName key="PL000000029396">寺</placeName>夢一丈夫，衣冠甚盛，熟視乃<persName key="A012167">長沙</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0826a27"/>也。<persName key="A012161">吾</persName>迎延坐，話舊傷感，如平生時。而謂<persName key="A012161">吾</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0826a28"/>曰：『後十年，<persName key="A012167">我</persName>之六世孫<persName key="A012163">廣</persName>當官於此<placeName key="PL000000029412">郡</placeName>，<persName key="A012161">師</persName>其<lb
ed="T" n="0826a29"/>念之。』乃問之曰：『<persName key="A012167">王</persName>今何為？』曰：『冥官極尊。』既<pb ed="T" n="0826b" xml:id="T50.2061.0826b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0826b01"/>而又泣曰：『<persName key="A012161">師</persName>存而<persName key="A012167">我</persName>之六世矣，悲夫！』<persName key="A012161">吾</persName>夢覺，<lb
ed="T" n="0826b02"/>因紀<persName key="A012163">君</persName>之名於經笥中，至去歲凡十年，乃<lb
ed="T" n="0826b03"/>以<persName key="A012163">君</persName>之名氏訪於<placeName key="PL000000029412">郡</placeName>人，尚怪<persName key="A012163">君</persName>之未至。昨<lb
ed="T" n="0826b04"/>因乞食里中，遇邑吏訪之，果得焉。及君之<lb
ed="T" n="0826b05"/>來，又依然<persName key="A012167">長沙</persName>之貌也。然自夢及今十一年<lb
ed="T" n="0826b06"/>矣！故訝<persName key="A012163">君</persName>之晚也。」已而悲惋，泣下數行，因<lb
ed="T" n="0826b07"/>出經笥示之。<persName key="A012163">廣</persName>再拜，願執屨錫為弟子。<lb
ed="T" n="0826b08"/><persName key="A012161">昭</persName>曰：「<persName key="A012163">君</persName>且去，翌日當再來。」<persName key="A012163">廣</persName>受教而還，明<lb
ed="T" n="0826b09"/>日至其居，<persName key="A012161">昭</persName>已遁去，莫知其適。時<date from-iso="+0816-02-06" key="j20191342019487" to-iso="+0817-01-24"><name>元和</name>十<lb
ed="T" n="0826b10"/>一年</date>也。至<date notBefore-iso="+0827-03-18" key="j20231922024000" notAfter-iso="+0829-06-03">大和初</date>，<persName key="A012163">廣</persName>為<placeName key="PL000000037154">巴州</placeName>掾，於山南道<lb
ed="T" n="0826b11"/>路逢<persName key="A012161">昭</persName>，驚喜再拜曰：「願棄官，請從<persName key="A012161">師</persName>為物<lb
ed="T" n="0826b12"/>外之遊。」<persName key="A012161">昭</persName>亦許之，其夕偕舍于逆旅。至天<lb
ed="T" n="0826b13"/>將曙，<persName key="A012163">廣</persName>早起而省<persName key="A012161">昭</persName>已去矣。<persName key="A012163">廣</persName>茫然若有<lb
ed="T" n="0826b14"/>所喪，神情沮敗，自是盡不知所往也。然<lb
ed="T" n="0826b15"/>則<persName key="A012161">昭</persName>自<date from-iso="+0526-01-31" key="j19132081913591" to-iso="+0527-02-18">梁普通七年生</date>，于時歲在丙午，下<lb
ed="T" n="0826b16"/>至<date from-iso="+0815-02-17" key="j20187802019133" to-iso="+0816-02-05">唐<name>元和</name>十年乙未</date>，凡二百九十年，則與<persName key="A012161">昭</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0826b17"/>言如合符契焉。</p>
    <p xml:id="pT50p0826b1801"><lb
ed="T" n="0826b18"/>系曰：<persName key="A012161">慧昭</persName>既三百年住世也，前不可測，後未<lb
ed="T" n="0826b19"/>可涯，與夫<persName key="A006022">賓頭羅睺尊</persName>者一貫，胡不念恩<lb
ed="T" n="0826b20"/>地之裔孫邪？通曰：「神仙隔一塵，猶未可與<lb
ed="T" n="0826b21"/>之遊。且<persName key="A012163">廣</persName>是具縛凡夫，<persName key="A012161">昭</persName>為度世上士，飛<lb
ed="T" n="0826b22"/>鳶與淵魚，蹤跡相遠，此何怪歟？」</p>
